des: If you are looking to sell, refinance your mortgage, or are just curious about the value of your home, Redefy Real Estate can help. We use our robust home valuation software to tell you an approximate value of your property, based on home sales in the area and unique attributes about your home. If you would like a more in-depth analysis after you have received your value, you can schedule a licensed real estate broker to come to your home.
